description: Come and experience Fire Truck Crepes where you will be served humongous, delicious crepes from on board our food / fire truck. Our crepes are 18" round and are filled with your choice of sweet or savory menu items. And for those who prefer gluten free, have no fear because we have created a gluten free batter just for youYou are welcome to nosh and go, or relax in our custom seating area from inside "Spartan" our 25 year old vintage fire truck.Reinventing the food truck, one humongous crepe at a time...book us for your next event!
name: Fire Truck Crepes
